"""Ensure ChemKED YAML is validated
        """
try:
    assert v.validate(properties)
except AssertionError:
    print(v.errors)
    assert False
pytest.mark.parametrize('properties', ['testfile_st.yaml',
    'testfile_st2.yaml', 'testfile_rcm.yaml', 'testfile_required.yaml',
    'testfile_uncertainty.yaml', 'testfile_rcm2.yaml'], indirect=['properties']
    )
